    <section id="about" class="section">
        <h2>About Question Hound <i><b>($QHND)</b></i></h2>
        <p><strong>Question Hound ($QHND) - This is Fine</strong> is a meme token built for those who embrace the chaos of bear markets. With <strong>100 million tokens</strong> and a <strong>5% tax on each transaction</strong>, $QHND is designed to reward players who thrive on timing and strategy.</p>
        <p>Here’s how the reward system works:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Every transaction has a <strong>5% tax</strong>, with <strong>2% added to liquidity</strong> for market stability.</li>
            <li>The remaining <strong>3% is redistributed</strong> to active traders:</li>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>2%</strong> goes to the <strong>last buyer/seller</strong> before the transaction.</li>
                <li><strong>1%</strong> goes to the <strong>buyer/seller before the last one</strong>.</li>
            </ul>
            <li>The reward depends on the next transaction: If it’s a <strong>buy</strong>, you’ll earn <strong>BNB</strong>. If it’s a <strong>sell</strong>, you’ll get <strong>more $QHND tokens</strong>!</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This creates an exciting game where timing is key. You never know when a whale might make a move—if you trade right before them, you’re in for a sweet reward!</p>
        <p><strong>The token for those who laugh through the flames. Get in, trade, and stay sharp—fortune favors the bold!</strong></p>
    </section>

